Catalogue tudo que você tem dentro do seu guarda-roupa! O KeepCloset te
ajuda a se sentir mais confiante ao se vestir, a fazer compras de forma consciente,
mostra todas suas roupas e acessórios de forma categorizada e personalizada por
você, oferece opções de guardar looks e inspirações, tem a opção de programar em um calendário todos os looks que deseja usar no mês, planeja seus looks e check-list para sua bagagem dentre vários outros extras como estatísticas de cores, roupas mais e menos usadas!

Disponível para Smartphones e Tablets.

RECURSOS:
CLOSET: adiciona suas próprias roupas e acessórios de forma categorizada
(categoria, cor, temperatura, marca e status);
FERRAMENTA DE REMOÇÃO DE FUNDO: extremamente fácil de usar e funcional
melhorando a visibilidade da peça;
LOOKS: fotos dos seus próprios looks categorizados por ocasião e quadros com
colagens de suas próprias roupas e acessórios como em revistas;
INSPIRAÇÕES: fotos de moda e beleza que te inspiram;
BACKUP NO iCLOUD: backup automático para proteger seus dados ou para uma
eventual troca de aparelho;
BAGAGEM: faça check-lists com itens diversos e looks montados para cada dia
de sua viagem;
CALENDÁRIO: Faça um planejamento do que gostaria de vestir num determinado
período;
PESQUISAR: Ferramenta para acesso rápido a palavras-chaves que deseja
encontrar dentro do seu closet;
ESTATÍSTICAS: Cores (gráfico pizza com informando as cores do seu closet),
roupas mais e menos usadas, dentre outros;
SEM LIMITE: adicione quantas peças, looks e inspirações que desejar;
CATEGORIAS: São criadas e personalizadas por você. Adicione quantas forem
necessárias. Categorias criadas e sem peças inclusas são automaticamente
excluídas;
CORES: Definidas automaticamente pelo aplicativo ao guardar a peça. Pode ser
alterada por você;
TEMPERATURA: categoria selecionada conforme o clima da roupa;
COMPARTILHE: compartilhe de forma rápida seus looks inspirações em redes
sociais, e-mail e whatsapp;
SUPORTE: tutoriais sobre recursos do aplicativo, dicas lifestyle, e-book dentre outros;
STATUS: Emprestou uma roupa?, Precisa de ajuste?, vai para doação? marque ela aqui e crie quantas categorias de status desejar;
MARCA: categorize qual a marca da sua roupa e descubra em estatísticas quais as suas prediletas.

Visite nosso site www.keepcloset.com.br para mais informações.

SketchCut PRO - Fast Cutting. The application for automatic calculation of cutting drawings of parts from flat sheets.

The app is designed with the features of cutting sheet materials (particleboard, MDF, glass, plastics, wood panels, etc.) both in the manual and on the machine.

Full version SketchCut. Without advertising.

The application functions are available:

- choice and change of cutting parameters (sheet size, blade width, offset from the edge of the sheet, etc.);

- edging (two types of edges);

- order information (order, material, order date, availability date);

- automatic cutting of sheets in accordance with the selected parameters;

- three different algorithms for calculating and optimizing layouts - to select the best option of cutting;

- automatic calculation of the area of parts and pieces, cut length, the length of the edges;

- display of the results in the .PDF file for printing;

- storing a list of parts and the cutting parameters on your device;

- metric system and Imperial units, with a simple conversion

With 20 millions of downloads worldwide Real Drift Car Racing is the most realistic drift game on mobile devices, and yet easy to control and fun to play thanks to an innovative drift helper.
Get ready to drive high performance cars (turbo or naturally aspirated) and make them drift at high speed in tracks designed specifically for drift racing.
Improve your racing and drifting skills and earn virtual money to tune and customize your car.
Race to battle the world record of the leaderboard or just for fun in the freeride mode.

FEATURES
• The most realistic drift racing simulation on mobile devices;
• Customizable difficulty: from total novice to professional drifter;
• Extensive customization options: change body color, body vinyl, rims model, rims color and tire signature;
• Extensive tuning options: increase engine power, add a turbo, change handling settings (weight distribution, camber angle etc.), change gear ratios and shift speed;
• Photo mode to share your coolest drifts with your friends;
• Realistic simulation of all aspect (engine, drivetrain, tires, etc.) of the car;
• Specific engine sound for every car with turbo whistle and blow off valve;
• Backfire effects with sounds;
• Accurate points calculation: earn points by drifting at high speed, at high drift angle and, by light touching walls during a drift;
• Online and local leaderboard to challenge your friends and people all over the world;
• Big training track to improve your drifting and racing skills;
• Cool dubstep soundtrack by Liquid Stranger and Simplify Recordings.
• 35 racing tracks specifically designed for drifting;
• 19 different cars with specific and realistic setup;
• Challenging career mode with 38 championships with growing difficulty;


GAMEPLAY
• Accelerometer (gyroscope) or touch steering mode;
• Slider or touch throttle;
• Automatic or manual transmission;
• Metric or Imperial units of measurement;


ADVANCED POINTS SYSTEM
Points grow proportionally to drift angle, drift time and speed.
There are also 2 different points multiplier: "Drift Combo" multiplier and "Proximity" multiplier.
Drift Combo multiplier is increased by 1 whenever points reach a power of 2000 (1000, 2000,4000, 8000 etc.). If you change drift direction, points are added to Total Points Indicator (located in the top left of the screen) and reset. If points reach every multiple of 2000 again, Drift Combo is increased by 1 again. This works only if you keep drifting without too long interruptions between one drift and the other (less than 1 second), otherwise Drift Combo multiplier will be reset to 1.
Proximity multiplier is increased when you drift with the back of the car near a wall (less than 1.5 meters) proportionally to closeness. You'll notice this bonus with a slow motion effect and a text showing the multiplier factor.
If you hit anything you'll lose your partial points and all multipliers.

We will update and improve Real Drift constantly. Please rate and give your feedback for further improvement of the game.
